🤔Q: Have #COVIDvaccines been causing deaths? 
💡A: To date, the CDC & FDA have found no clinical evidence that #COVID19 vaccination contributed to patient deaths reported in #VAERS. Learn more on the CDC's website to help fight #vaccine misinformation!
